  "description": "<i>My Little Flufties</i> is a 3D life simulator in the line of Tamagochi. Aimed at children aged 5-9, gamers can choose between 5 imaginary creatures. You must nourish, wash, educate and amuse the creatures to keep the game going.<br><br>The fairy-like 3D world contains several attractions like swings and slides. Next to that, there are also 5 mini-games available in the game:<ul><li>Mole-o-matic: jump on the head of the moles to stun them.</li>\n<li>Shoot the balloons: shoot with a peashooter to pop coloured balloons.</li>\n<li>Fish-o-matic: catch fish with a fishing net.</li>\n<li>Hopscotch: jump on the good squares to advance.</li>\n<li>Find the Tweet-Tweet: find 4 birds hidden in the game's world.</li></ul>The game uses a full 3D engine but with a traditional drawing style, similar to <a href=\"https://www.mobygames.com/game/kami\">?kami</a>.",
